JONES v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 45,

September Term, 1960.]

Decided January 17, 1961.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott and Horney, JJ.

PER Curiam.

The application for leave to appeal is denied for the rea*643sons set forth in detail in the memorandum and order of Judge Warnken denying post conviction relief.

Application denied.
